name: facility_id
description: Unique number automatically generated at Children and Family Services to identify an individual facility.

name: program_type
description: FDC = Family Day Care; GFDC = Group Family Day Care; SACC = School Age Child Care; DCC = Day Care Center; SDCC = Small Day Care Center

name: region_code
description: ARO =Albany Regional Office; BRO =Buffalo Regional Office; LIRO = Long Island Regional Office; NYCDOHMH =NYC Department of Health and Mental Hygiene; RRO = Rochester Regional Office; SRO = Syracuse Regional Office; YRO = Spring Valley Regional Office

name: county
description: County in which the facility is located.

name: facility_status
description: License = GFDC or DCC; Registration = FDC, SACC, SDCC; Pending Revocation = recommended for revocation; Pending Revocation & Denial = recommended for revocation/denial; Pending Denial = recommended for denial; Suspended = may not care for children

name: facility_name
description: DBA (legal entity/doing business as) name or Legal Name (last name, first name)

name: facility_opened_date
description: Date the facility began operation.

name: license_issue_date
description: Date a license was issued for the facility

name: license_expiration_date
description: Date the license for the facility will expire.

name: address_omitted
description: As a result of a bill signed into law (Chapter 354 of the Laws of 2009), the dataset omits addresses for those child care providers who have “opted out” from having their addresses and map included. "Y" indicates they opted out, blank indicates they did not.

name: city
description: City the program is located in.

name: state
description: State the program is located in.

name: zip_code
description: Zip code of the city the program is located in.

name: phone_number
description: Phone number of the program. Excluded for providers who have unlisted phone numbers

name: provider_name
description: Name of On-Site Provider/Director (Last name, First name). If not approved, “There is no approved Director/On-Site Provider at this site” appears

name: school_district_name
description: Name of School District in which Program is located

name: capacity_description
description: This only applies if the Program Type is Family Day Care (FDC) or Group Family Day Care (GFDC).

name: infant_capacity
description: For DCC, total number of children up to 18 months of age

name: toddler_capacity
description: For DCC, total number of children ages 18 months to 36 months

name: preschool_capacity
description: For DCC, total number of children at least 3 years of age who are not yet enrolled in kindergarten or a higher grade

name: school_age_capacity
description: For DCC and SACC, total number of children who are under 13 years of age who are enrolled in kindergarten or a higher grade

name: total_capacity
description: Refer to the data dictionary found in the About tab for the definition of Total Capacity.

name: additional_information
description: Overview information of the program and violation history. This does not include the results of inspections where no violations are cited.

name: street_number
description: Street number portion of the address of the program. Excluded if provider has opted out

name: street_name
description: Street name of the address of the program. Excluded if provider has opted out

name: latitude
description: As a result of a bill signed into law (Chapter 354 of the Laws of 2009), the dataset omits addresses for those child care providers who have “opted out” from having their addresses and map included.

name: longitude
description: As a result of a bill signed into law (Chapter 354 of the Laws of 2009), the dataset omits addresses for those child care providers who have “opted out” from having their addresses and map included.

name: floor
description: Floor detail of the address of the program. Excluded if provider has opted out or if it does not apply.

name: apartment
description: Apartment info of the address of the program. Excluded if provider has opted out or it does not apply.

name: phone_extension
description: Phone extension for the program phone number. Excluded if provider has opted out, has unlisted phone number or if there is none.

name: phone_number_omitted
description: Excluded for providers who have unlisted phone numbers. ",Y" indicates they opted out or have an unlisted number, blank indicates they did not.

name: additional_address
description: Additional address information for the program. Excluded if provider has opted out or if it does not apply.

name: record_date
description: time when record was added

name: ingestion_timestamp
description: time when record was ingested
